title: Fearne Cotton shares adorable snap of baby daughter Honey with daddy
text:
Fearne Cotton shares adorable snap of baby daughter Honey with daddy Published Sunday, Oct 4 2015, 19:37 BST | By Helen Fear | Fearne Cotton has given us a glimpse into her family life in a series of new photos. And they are bound to make you coo and cluck! 
© Instagram / fearnecotton In a rare snap of their newborn daughter Honey who was born in September, dad Jesse Wood looks absolutely smitten.The black and white photograph shows rock guitarist Jesse - son of Rolling Stones legend Ronnie - staring into the eyes of his tiny baby creation as he lays beside her in bed.Alongside the heartmelting picture, 34-year-old Fearne simply posted a heart emotion and the words: "Dad & daughter."A ! 
© Instagram / fearnecotton While the picture exhibits a scene of domestic bliss, Fearne admitted earlier the same week that she was battling extreme tiredness.She tweeted her 6.51million followers: "Sleep deprivation just got real. Just took me 10 mins to get my car off the driveway as I FORGOT how to drive my car."We've all been there, Fearne! 
© Instagram / fearnecotton The proud mum-of-two also joked with fans that "after two weeks on planet earth Honey definitely has more clothes than me".The former Radio One DJ also has a two-year-old son called Rex.Last month, she posted a selfie showing her face decorated with sticker gems courtesy of the toddler. 
© Instagram / fearnecotton She also shared a picture of her slider slippers... Personalised with her married name Mrs Wood.No wonder down-to-earth Fearne has so many followers on social media.Fans appreciate her posts, with one gushing: "I love your lifestyle and how real you are. I don't have children yet but looking at your pics makes me see how beautiful and scary in a good way it must be. Cheers love!"
